text: Nizhneshakarovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Saraysinsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 74 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 28 km from Sterlibashevo, 13 km from Yelimbetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Nizhneshakarovo
